The International Revolutionary People's Guerrilla Forces (IRPGF) is a collective of anarchist fighters from around the world. Its formation was announced on 31 March 2017. According to the group, their goals are to defend the social revolution in Rojava in northern Syria, and spread anarchism.
The IRPGF are part of the International Freedom Battalion since April 2017. Turkish media have described them as a terrorist organization and part of the network of the outlawed Kurdistan Workers' Party.
